{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Thales-D1-A-Card-API-to-Modernise-Card-Issuance","level":2,"text":"Thales D1 - A Card API to Modernise Card Issuance"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"At Thales we firmly believe that end users around the world deserve the best card experience! This is the reason why we fight to remove the border between physical and digital; this is why we want to bring real-time experience in card issuance & payment and this is also why we want to give back control to the end user."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To achieve this goal, we launched D1: "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"a modern card issuing platform assembling banking core systems with modern digital components"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By leveraging "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"our cloud native design, exposing modern back-end and front-end APIs","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", we drop a significant chunk of the complexity for issuers such as payment network integration, real-time circulation of data, security certifications and regulations compliance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thales puts card issuers in the new digital league in record time."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"externalID":"D1","symbolKind":"module","title":"D1","role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"D1"}],"roleHeading":"Framework"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Legal","title":"Legal","identifiers":["doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/TermsOfUse"]},{"title":"Classes","identifiers":["doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/CardAsset","doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/CardControlSettings","doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/CardDetailsUI","doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/CardLimitSettings","doc:\/\/D1\/documentation\/D1\/CardService","doc:\/\